hopobject.body: Where are you from? nitroforce titan 1000 youtube Hiroki Kuroda is a free agent, but he says he has not made any decisions about his future. "Anything's possible," he said through a translator, indicating returning, retiring or pitching in Japan. He did say that any perception that he wants to pitch one final year in his homeland is not necessarily true. "I always take one year at a time," he said. "That's not something that I particularly plan to do."
